description: Sweet Memories Ice Cream has 2 Original 1960's Good Humor Ice Cream Trucks available for your next event.We are perfect for Birthday partys, Block partys, Fairs, Corporate Events or Community celebrations. At Sweet Memories Ice Cream, We provide you and your guests with the finest premium ice cream and novelties from Good Humor, Popsicle, Dove, Klondike and Haagen DazsSweet Memories Ice Cream concentrates on serving fine products with good old fashioned service customary of Good Humor. Our trucks come with a state of the art audio system. Our truck has its own lighting and is sure to draw a crowd. A lot of customers tell us that this was the truck and ice cream they remember as kids. Our servers are courteous and uniformed and will keep the service area clean.
name: Sweet Memories Ice Cream
